<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>
        Information - Sendmate
    </title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
    <style>
        main div ul li {
            list-style: disc;
        }

        main div ol {
            padding-left: 5rem !important;
        }

        main div ol li {
            list-style: square;
        }

        main div li ul li{
            margin-left: 5rem !important;
            list-style: circle;
        }

        main div h2 {
            font-size: 1.5rem !important;
            margin-top: 3rem !important;
            margin-bottom: 1rem !important;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="wrapper">

        <% if (!user) { %>
            <%- include('partials/nav') %> <!-- Nav for logged-in users -->
                <% } else { %>
                    <%- include('partials/nav_users') %><!-- Nav for guests -->
                        <% } %>
                            <main>
                                <div class="information-div container mx-auto flex justify-between py-2 px-8"
                                    style="flex-direction: column;">
                                    <ul>
                                        <li>
                                            <h2 style="margin-top: 0 !important;"><b>Step 1: Registration</b></h2>
                                        </li>
                                    </ul>
                                    <ol>
                                        <li> <b>Visit Homepage:</b> Click on the "Sign Up" button.</li>
                                        <br>
                                        <li> <b>Fill in Your Details:</b> Enter your Username, Email and Password.</li>
                                        <br>
                                        <li> <b>Confirm Registration: </b> Check your email for a confirmation link and
                                            click it to activate your account.
                                        </li>
                                    </ol>

                                    <ul>
                                        <li>
                                            <h2><b>Step 2: Login</b></h2>
                                        </li>
                                    </ul>
                                    <ol>
                                        <li><b>Go to the Login Page:</b> Click on the "Login" button on the homepage.
                                        </li>
                                        <br>
                                        <li><b>Enter Your Credentials:</b> Input your registered email and password.
                                        </li>
                                        <br>
                                        <li><b>Access Your Dashboard:</b> Once logged in, you'll be directed to your
                                            user dashboard.</li>
                                    </ol>

                                    <ul>
                                        <li>
                                            <h2><b>Step 3: Creating a Post (Sender)</b></h2>
                                        </li>
                                    </ul>
                                    <ol>
                                        <li><b>Navigate to Create Post:</b> Click on the "Create Post" button in your
                                            dashboard.</li>
                                        <br>
                                        <li><b>Fill in the Parcel Details:</b> Provide information such as:</li>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li>Parcel Description</li>
                                            <li>Size and Weight</li>
                                            <li>Pickup Location</li>
                                            <li>Delivery Location</li>
                                            <li>Preffered Delivery Time</li>
                                        </ul>
                                        <br>
                                        <li><b>Set Payment Terms:</b> Indicate how much you are willing to pay the
                                            traveler.</li>
                                        <br>
                                        <li><b>Publish Your Post:</b> Review the details and click "Post" to make it
                                            visible to travelers.</li>
                                    </ol>

                                    <ul>
                                        <li>
                                            <h2><b>Step 4: Browsing and Approaching (Traveler)</b></h2>
                                        </li>
                                    </ul>
                                    <ol>
                                        <li><b>View Available Posts:</b> Go to the "Available Posts" section in your
                                            dashboard.</li>
                                        <br>
                                        <li><b>Select a Parcel:</b> Browse through the listed parcels and click on one
                                            that interests you.</li>
                                        <br>
                                        <li><b>Contact the Sender:</b> Use the "Contact" option to send a message or
                                            request more details.</li>
                                    </ol>

                                    <ul>
                                        <li>
                                            <h2><b>Step 5: Agreement and Consent Form</b></h2>
                                        </li>
                                    </ul>
                                    <ol>
                                        <li><b>Negotiate Terms:</b> Discuss the details, such as delivery time and
                                            payment, with the sender.</li>
                                        <br>
                                        <li><b>Confirm Agreement:</b> Once both parties are satisfied, agree on the
                                            terms verbally or through the platform's
                                            messaging feature.</li>
                                        <br>
                                        <li><b>Fill Out the Consent Form:</b> Complete a digital consent form that
                                            outlines:
                                            <ul>
                                                <li>Delivery Details</li>
                                                <li>Payment Agreement</li>
                                                <li>Responsibilities of both parties</li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </li>

                                        <br>
                                        <li><b>Submit the Form:</b> Ensure both parties sign and submit the consent form
                                            through the platform.</li>
                                    </ol>

                                    <ul>
                                        <li>
                                            <h2><b>Step 6: Delivery Process</b></h2>
                                        </li>
                                    </ul>
                                    <ol>
                                        <li><b>Pickup the Parcel:</b> The traveler picks up the parcel from the sender's
                                            specified location.</li>
                                        <br>
                                        <li><b>Delivery:</b> The traveler delivers the parcel to the agreed destination.
                                        </li>
                                        <br>
                                        <li><b>Complete Transaction:</b> After successful delivery, the sender confirms
                                            receipt, and the payment is
                                            processed.</li>
                                    </ol>

                                    <ul>
                                        <li>
                                            <h2><b>Step 7: Feedback and Rating</b></h2>
                                        </li>
                                    </ul>
                                    <ol>
                                        <li><b>Rate Your Experience:</b> After the transaction, both parties can rate
                                            each other and leave feedback.</li>
                                        <br>
                                        <li><b>Improve the Community:</b> Use the feedback to enhance future
                                            interactions on the platform.</li>
                                    </ol>
                                </div>


                            </main>
                            <%- include('partials/footer') %>
    </div>

</body>

</html>